About

Fantastic (small) Collection Of Customised Cars & Motorcycles
Jun 2024 Couples
For me this was fantastic to actually visit Counts Kustoms in Las Vegas, and its free to enter and gaze over Danny The Count Kokers private collection of custom cars & motorcycles. Im from the UK and have been watching the TV series, filmed at the premises, Counting Cars since it appeared on our television screens.
It is a great collection, quite small, but just to see the paint work and custom work the guys have put into each vehicle is amazing.

The only downsides for me is that it would have been nice to have each vehicle have its own marker to state what model & type it was, instead of calling to the show room staff members and asking these guys. Also it would have been nice to have had a meet & greet day to possibly chat to Danny and Co. Some staff members say they were not here on the day I visited, other staff members say they were but possibly not available ?

Anyhow it was great to be at the showroom after seeing each episode of the TV series.
Written July 9, 2024
